103
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:40,160
It's not too bad up here on the roof of the car, is it?

104
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:44,560
Because the night view is so nice.

105
00:06:45,860 --> 00:06:47,260
This is the place

106
00:06:47,260 --> 00:06:50,560
