107
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,860
It's over here?

108
00:06:51,860 --> 00:06:52,960
Wait a second.

109
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:55,660
Then, the trick that I was thinking of a while ago...

110
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:57,160
Hey, everyone!

111
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:59,860
