137
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,360
Yeah.

138
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,860
Just as I thought!

139
00:08:13,860 --> 00:08:15,360
Yeah.

140
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,460
We haven't been using it recently

141
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:18,360
